%N A048923 Indices of octagonal numbers which are also 9-gonal.
%C A048923 As n increases, this sequence is approximately geometric with common ratio r = lim_{n->oo} a(n)/a(n-1) = (sqrt(6) + sqrt(7))^4 = 337 + 52*sqrt(42). - _Ant King_, Jan 03 2012
